      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im 5 months pregnant and i have such a bad sinus infection... my head is pounding and i cant breathe through my nose at all. i have some pseudoephedrine (sudafed) in my cabinet, is it okay if i take some of that to help with the congestion??",
