      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should probably call someone but i just really need something that works now. i saw online that some people use ciprofloxacin for sinus stuff and it says it's effective. if i just take one or two pills to see if it helps the pressure, is it really that much of a risk? like it's not like i'm taking a whole course or anything. im just looking for some quick relief so i can get through my shift.",
